Text: Order Confirmation Dr Pepper Big Championship GameBig Ticket Holders Thank you for ordering Dr Pepper Big Football Championship tickets We have received your application and are in the process of assigning your seats Your tickets and parking will be mailed by the end of October If you would like to know your seat assignment please send an email mailto requesting your location and we will respond as soon as your seat has been assignedor contact the ticket office after Wednesday October Thank you for supporting the Big Conference Thank you
